INSTALL A PACKAGE

---
- hosts: *ip address or group name of ip addresses*
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: *Give this playbook function a name/description*
      yum:
        name: *package to install*














INSTALL MULTIPLE PACKAGES

---
- hosts: *ip address or group name of ip addresses*
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: *Give this playbook function a name/description*
      yum:
        name:
          - *package*
          - *package*
          - *package*
          - *package* and so on...












REMOVE A PACKAGE

---
- hosts: *ip address or group name of ip addresses*
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: *Give this playbook function a name/description*
      yum:
        name: *package*
        state: absent














UPDATE SERVERS

---
- hosts: *ip address or group name of ip addresses*
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: *Give this playbook function a name/description*
      yum:
        name: "*"
        state: latest